<subSubSection id="50120F06400B7BB037560D6334CA6C2B" pageId="50" pageNumber="51" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="62FE731268C10CE3576461C32D5F15D9" pageId="50" pageNumber="51">
<taxonomicName id="351030C191F150507A81DFB684D55C16" authority="Giglio-Tos, 1891" authorityName="Giglio-Tos" authorityYear="1891" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Omegasyrphus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Omegasyrphus" order="Diptera" pageId="50" pageNumber="51" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Omegasyrphus</taxonomicName>
Giglio-Tos, 1891: 4. Type species: 
<taxonomicName id="1F5DFA449150DBA5664913CCE1EE0A16" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Microdon" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Microdon coarctatus" order="Diptera" pageId="50" pageNumber="51" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="coarctatus">Microdon coarctatus</taxonomicName>
Loew, 1864: 74, by subsequent designation of 
<bibRefCitation id="61F7D402829263297133461B58A212CC" author="Giglio-Tos, E" journalOrPublisher="Bollettino dei Musei Zoologia ed Anatomia comparata" pageId="83" pageNumber="84" pagination="1 - 3" title="Sui due generi di Sirfifi Rhopalosyrphus ed Omegasyrphus." volume="118" year="1892">Giglio-Tos (1892</bibRefCitation>
